'''比弗顿学区'''('''Beaverton School District''')是[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]]的[[学区|学区]]，总部在{{link-en|比弗顿 (俄勒冈州)|Beaverton, Oregon|比弗顿}}。<ref>"[https://www.beaverton.k12.or.us/depts/tchlrn/ELL/Chinese%20Documents/FAQ%20Transportation%20Chinese.pdf FAQ-常见问题]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}." 比弗顿学区.</ref> 比弗顿学区營運33間小学、8間初中和5間高中，学生人數達40,568人(50%是少数民族)。<ref>"[https://www.beaverton.k12.or.us/about/quick-facts District Quick Facts] {{Wayback|url=https://www.beaverton.k12.or.us/about/quick-facts |date=20150707082646 }}." 比弗顿学区.</ref>

